title: Case iH 335 Magnum Row-Crop Tractor
item_description:
Case iH 335 Magnum Row-Crop Tractor

The sale of this item is subject to the sellers confirmation.

  • Manufacturer: Case iH
  • Model: 335 Magnum
  • Year of Manufacture: 2008
  • Hours: 3336
  • Tractor Type: Tractor
  • Drive: 4 Wheel Drive
  • Number of Tires: 8
  • Front Tire Size: 540/65 R34
  • Rear Tire Size: 710/70R42
  • Fuel Type: Diesel
  • Transmission: 19-Speed Full Powershift

The following information was obtained from tractordata.com and has not been verified by West Auctions:

  • Engine: CNH 8.9L 6-cyl diesel
  • Engine power: 330 hp
  • PTO (claimed): 275 hp
  • Drawbar (tested) 243.25 hp
  • Mechanical:
    • Four-Wheel Drive
    • Power Steering
    • Differential hydraulic wet disc brakes
    • Cab standard with heat and air conditioning
  • Fuel Capacity: 180 Gal
  • Hydraulic System Capacity: 45.5 Gal
  • Dimensions and Tires:
    • Wheelbase: 118.3"
    • Weight: 21350 Lbs

Link to tractor data page: https://www.tractordata.com/farm-tractors/005/6/3/5630-caseih-magnum-335.html

CARB Off-Road Diesel Disclosure Statement: “When operated in California, any off-road diesel vehicle may be subject to the California Air Resources Board In-Use Off-road Diesel Vehicle Regulation. It therefore could be subject to retrofit or accelerated turnover requirements to reduce emissions of air pollutants. For more information, please visit the California Air Resources Board website at http://www.arb.ca.gov/msprog/ordiesel/ordiesel.htm.”
